1
00:00:20,710 --> 00:00:21,550
Huahua,

2
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:23,280
don't be scared.

3
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:25,640
Let me give you a hug.

4
00:00:27,350 --> 00:00:28,190
Just one hug.

5
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:31,760
Liu, come on.

6
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:33,080
Liu.

7
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:34,350
Another toast.

8
00:00:42,110 --> 00:00:42,950
Huahua…

9
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:45,120
Huahua…

10
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:46,960
My Huahua…

11
00:00:48,430 --> 00:00:49,840
Let's play.

12
00:01:02,390 --> 00:01:03,240
Fire!

13
00:01:03,350 --> 00:01:04,280
Fire!

14
00:01:04,430 --> 00:01:06,400
Fire! Help!

15
00:01:08,790 --> 00:01:09,630
My meds.

16
00:01:10,230 --> 00:01:11,430
My meds.

17
00:01:13,870 --> 00:01:14,710
My meds.

18
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,280
Fire!

19
00:01:34,350 --> 00:01:35,190
Fire!

20
00:01:51,790 --> 00:01:52,640
In Qingcheng,

21
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:55,150
no one talks to me like that.

22
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,480
You want your money back?

23
00:01:58,150 --> 00:01:59,280
Come on!

24
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,430
Come take it!

25
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,200
Give me a hand.

26
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,520
Get rid of this jerk.

27
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:40,430
Where's the money you promised?

28
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,120
You...

29
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,080
You're insane.

30
00:02:58,150 --> 00:02:59,470
If it weren't for you,

31
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,520
my daughter wouldn't be dead.

32
00:03:31,780 --> 00:03:35,660
=The Hidden Truth=

33
00:03:35,660 --> 00:03:38,300
=Episode 10=

34
00:03:38,300 --> 00:03:40,700
(Serve the People - Mao Zedong)

35
00:03:44,820 --> 00:03:45,660
(Teahouse Shareholder; Dog shelter)

36
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,910
Can we confirm it's the same person?

37
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,120
I think it's him.

38
00:04:05,590 --> 00:04:08,150
Bai. Bai Qiming.

39
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,840
He hid for 15 years.

40
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:15,190
How could there be no trace?

41
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,560
Could he have left the country?

42
00:04:21,270 --> 00:04:22,950
Then he crossed illegally.

43
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,160
Now that he's back,

44
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:26,870
his target is likely Wang Li.

45
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:28,270
Or even

46
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:29,680
his daughter.

47
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,600
The dog thieves' handler
was Zhang Ming.

48
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:43,600
Zhang Ming had someone above him.

49
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:49,360
But Master,

50
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,950
just like we thought,

51
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:54,480
Li Xu's deeply tied to Bai.

52
00:04:55,870 --> 00:04:57,190
In that case,

53
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,560
it raises the odds

54
00:04:59,190 --> 00:05:01,190
that Zhang Ming, Bai, and Li Xu

55
00:05:01,190 --> 00:05:03,040
were all working together.

56
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,120
After that day,

57
00:05:06,310 --> 00:05:08,870
Hongyun Restaurant suddenly shut down.

58
00:05:09,190 --> 00:05:10,920
Wang Li and the staff

59
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,040
never showed up again.

60
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:14,560
If these groups met,

61
00:05:15,070 --> 00:05:17,190
something big must've happened.

62
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,800
Is Zhang Ming's handler Wang Li or Bai?

63
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,750
We can't be sure.

64
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:23,600
What we do know is

65
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,750
that Zhang Ming is missing.

66
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:37,390
We should start

67
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,070
where he disappeared.

68
00:05:39,870 --> 00:05:42,000
That's what I thought too.

69
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,800
So I went to Hongyun.

70
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:48,240
Guess what I saw.

71
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:06,120
What are you looking at?

72
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,510
(Closed Until Further Notice)

73
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:09,120
Big sign here. Can't you read?

74
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:10,800
Why are you closed?

75
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:12,680
Felt like it. Any of your business?

76
00:06:14,270 --> 00:06:15,160
Where's Wang Li?

77
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:16,480
Where's everyone else?

78
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,190
Wang Li isn't the owner anymore.

79
00:06:18,190 --> 00:06:20,040
Where he went is none of my concern.

80
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,720
Wang Li sold the place to Li Xu?

81
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:24,910
Exactly.

82
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,480
Yimo once told me

83
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:30,390
how much Wang Li cared about it.

84
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,750
Selling it suddenly?

85
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:34,880
Something's off.

86
00:06:37,310 --> 00:06:39,240
I called Xu Qiang too.

87
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,630
Same story.

88
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:42,480
No one knows where Zhang Ming is.

89
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:45,310
Zhang Ming missing.

90
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:48,360
Restaurant closed.

91
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,390
They're connected.

92
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:51,840
Master.

93
00:06:52,390 --> 00:06:54,390
I checked Zhang Ming's family.

94
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:56,160
Only his mother's left.

95
00:06:56,510 --> 00:06:57,870
Long-term hospital patient.

96
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,480
Bedridden.

97
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,800
He hasn't shown up for days, right?

98
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:05,190
Three to five days, at least.

99
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,270
We find it strange too.

100
00:07:07,590 --> 00:07:09,480
They say long illness
tests a child's devotion.

101
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,720
But whenever he had time off,

102
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,160
he came to the hospital.

103
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:13,800
His mother's illness

104
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,310
has been treated here

105
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,630
in our hospital

106
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,000
for over a decade.

107
00:07:18,950 --> 00:07:21,070
This stay's been long.

108
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:23,560
Zhang Ming's been a devoted son,

109
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:26,000
going to the hospital often.

110
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:28,070
To vanish this long,

111
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,600
that's not normal.

112
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:33,000
Either he's hiding with a new plan

113
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:33,870
from his handler,

114
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,430
or he's been killed.

115
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:41,240
Pull everything on Zhang Ming again.

116
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:42,190
Full profile.

117
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,750
He's a key figure right now.

118
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,870
There's no way he left without a trace,

119
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,310
then just disappeared like that.

120
00:08:01,310 --> 00:08:02,870
The police called me.

121
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,310
I told them what you said.

122
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,080
Good.

123
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:11,240
Why did we shut down?

124
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:14,800
Where's Zhang Ming?

125
00:08:19,310 --> 00:08:20,560
I'll be honest.

126
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:22,590
Zhang Ming

127
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:27,430
teamed up with Bai a long time ago.

128
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:30,790
Back then,

129
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,630
when we buried Bai,

130
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:36,600
Zhang Ming realized he wasn't dead

131
00:08:37,270 --> 00:08:38,600
and let him go.

132
00:08:40,750 --> 00:08:43,080
Now Zhang Ming can't handle it.

133
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:46,000
He ran off with Bai.

134
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,000
I'm closing up.

135
00:08:56,510 --> 00:08:58,030
You've been staring. Which one?

136
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,240
Bai's back this time

137
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,320
to kill us.

138
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:13,000
So I gave the restaurant

139
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,150
to Li Xu,

140
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,280
hoping he'd

141
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:21,390
deal with Bai.

142
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,720
If Bai lives,

143
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:30,240
none of us will have peace.

144
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,630
What's your plan?

145
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:49,790
Strike first.

146
00:09:52,870 --> 00:09:54,030
Kill Bai.

147
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,600
We did it once back then.

148
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,280
Now,

149
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:04,360
we do it again now.

150
00:10:10,030 --> 00:10:10,870
Ali.

151
00:10:11,150 --> 00:10:12,670
The past is the past.

152
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:14,550
This is murder.

153
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,910
It's no small matter.

154
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:19,240
Isn't there another way?

155
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,120
I put Hongyun on the line.

156
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,550
My entire fortune.

157
00:10:23,630 --> 00:10:24,910
If there were another way,

158
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:26,080
would I do this?

159
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,080
But what if

160
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,600
there's a turn we're missing?

161
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,150
If we cross this line,

162
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:32,510
there's no going back.

163
00:10:34,790 --> 00:10:36,270
Let karma get Bai?

164
00:10:38,510 --> 00:10:40,200
Right now it's either him

165
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:42,240
or it's us.

166
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,790
No middle ground.

167
00:10:48,670 --> 00:10:49,510
Qiang.

168
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,720
I ask you one thing.

169
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:57,120
Watch over Yimo.

170
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:00,630
Keep her safe.

171
00:11:18,910 --> 00:11:20,120
Here.

172
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:22,270
Zhang Ming's mother, Lin Guifen.

173
00:11:22,270 --> 00:11:24,120
All her hospital records.

174
00:11:24,250 --> 00:11:25,110
Thanks.

175
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:25,960
No problem.

176
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:28,510
Look here.

177
00:11:30,180 --> 00:11:31,700
(Ultrasound Report; Lin Guifen)

178
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:37,960
Zhao.

179
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,440
Same routine.

180
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:40,920
Thanks.

181
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:41,990
Sure thing.

182
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:46,080
Tang Tang. Your master is over there.

183
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,000
Thanks, Mr. Li.

184
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,390
Ran all morning, I'm starving.

185
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,150
Got anything?

186
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:55,320
I pulled

187
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:57,480
all the medical records with Zhang.

188
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,560
And found something.

189
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:00,240
You always talk

190
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:03,030
while eating when anxious.

191
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:04,510
You'll gulp down air.

192
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:06,080
Swallow, then speak.

193
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:06,990
Okay.

194
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:07,960
I'll report first.

195
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,200
Zhang Ming

196
00:12:11,550 --> 00:12:13,360
lived very simply.

197
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:16,630
Basically restaurant to hospital.

198
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:19,670
Poor family background.

199
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:21,270
His biggest expense

200
00:12:21,270 --> 00:12:22,550
is his mother's treatment.

201
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:23,870
His mother, Lin Guifen,

202
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,120
has been treated

203
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,720
for 15 years.

204
00:12:27,390 --> 00:12:29,080
When we pulled up her medical records,

205
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:31,200
we found something interesting.

206
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:33,510
Your dumplings.

207
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:34,960
Thanks, Mr. Li.

208
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,960
- All served, enjoy.
- Thanks.

209
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,030
Alright.

210
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:39,120
Here.

211
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,480
Wipe my hands. Okay.

212
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,280
Here, Master.

213
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:57,870
(Ultrasound Report; Lin Guifen)
His mom

214
00:12:57,910 --> 00:12:59,510
started treatment here 15 years ago.

215
00:12:59,630 --> 00:13:01,080
Three years ago,

216
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:03,320
she was hospitalized when it worsened.

217
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:04,670
But before that,

218
00:13:04,670 --> 00:13:05,630
she'd been treated there

219
00:13:05,630 --> 00:13:07,120
for over 10 years.

220
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,480
This hospital isn't cheap.

221
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,290
The costs over the years

222
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:13,790
must've been huge.

223
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,630
Before this,

224
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:17,390
she was at a rural clinic.

225
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,480
Which means,

226
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:21,240
fifteen years ago,

227
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:23,270
Zhang Ming suddenly had money.

228
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:25,030
Enough to move his mother

229
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:26,550
to the city

230
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:28,750
and pay for treatment

231
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:31,630
continuously, until now.

232
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,600
Fifteen years ago?

233
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:39,150
The exact same time frame.

234
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,440
Coincidence?

235
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:43,960
It can't be.

236
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,720
This is not a coincidence.

237
00:13:47,630 --> 00:13:48,470
Captain,

238
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:49,750
can I eat now?

239
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,160
Eat.

240
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:56,870
Tang Tang.

241
00:13:57,030 --> 00:13:58,030
Just looking for you.

242
00:13:58,150 --> 00:13:59,870
Zhang Ming's call records are in.

243
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,840
Leave them with me.

244
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:03,680
Okay.

245
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:13,700
(Caller; Receiver; Qingcheng)

246
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:21,140
(Caller; Receiver; Qingcheng)

247
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:23,270
Stop chewing your pen cap.

248
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:27,840
You just never listen.

249
00:14:28,150 --> 00:14:29,080
Okay, I'll stop.

250
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:32,920
What's on your mind?

251
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:34,840
Just checking.

252
00:14:37,270 --> 00:14:39,510
We've got all the case leads.

253
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:41,030
Why the long face?

254
00:14:41,670 --> 00:14:42,510
I'm fine.

255
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:47,080
Back at lunch time,

256
00:14:47,390 --> 00:14:48,790
you were full of confidence.

257
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,320
Master.

258
00:14:53,550 --> 00:14:54,870
I'm just thinking

259
00:14:55,510 --> 00:14:58,440
our clues mostly line up.

260
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,600
Pretty much.

261
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,320
But Zhang Ming's missing.

262
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:03,200
Without him, we can't prove anything.

263
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:06,000
Wang Li's people

264
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:08,120
are clearly hiding something.

265
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:10,270
We haven't cracked them yet.

266
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,240
There's another angle

267
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:18,200
you haven't pursued.

268
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:27,390
Master.

269
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:30,000
Fifteen years ago,

270
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:32,360
Wang Yimo was just a kid.

271
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:35,790
She couldn't have been involved.

272
00:15:36,150 --> 00:15:38,150
If I bring her in, what do I even ask?

273
00:15:38,510 --> 00:15:39,350
Besides,

274
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:41,360
she's been studying away from home

275
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,720
all these years.

276
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:45,320
Even if Wang Li broke the law,

277
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:47,120
it has nothing to do with her.

278
00:16:00,550 --> 00:16:02,120
Didn't you already have a theory?

279
00:16:10,750 --> 00:16:12,630
You've been spaced out lately.

280
00:16:12,790 --> 00:16:14,390
What matters most in investigations?

281
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,480
Eliminate the impossible.

282
00:16:16,750 --> 00:16:18,030
Even if you don't want to,

283
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:19,360
you have to face the facts.

284
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:20,270
Face the truth.

285
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,680
Master.

286
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,840
What do I ask her?

287
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:29,480
I don't even know where to start.

288
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:31,030
So why even bring her in?

289
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:33,120
She worked at the restaurant.

290
00:16:33,150 --> 00:16:34,910
Calls with Xu Qiang and Zhang Ming

291
00:16:34,910 --> 00:16:36,390
are normal.

292
00:16:36,550 --> 00:16:37,390
I...

293
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:40,120
I just wanted to discuss

294
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,840
to see if there's a new direction.

295
00:16:41,910 --> 00:16:43,200
It's right there.

296
00:16:43,390 --> 00:16:45,270
Ask first, then see what comes out.

297
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:49,390
How many times do I have to say it?

298
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:51,150
You're a detective.

299
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:52,120
You're working a case.

300
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,550
This isn't about personal feelings.

301
00:16:55,390 --> 00:16:56,670
Personal?

302
00:16:56,790 --> 00:16:58,630
That's harsh.

303
00:16:59,030 --> 00:17:01,480
I'm just trying to talk it through

304
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:03,750
to see if there's a new angle.

305
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:05,510
The direction's been pointed out.

306
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:08,790
What are you two arguing about?

307
00:17:09,510 --> 00:17:10,680
Heard the racket

308
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:12,000
from outside.

309
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,270
Still not home, Mr. Qin?

310
00:17:16,310 --> 00:17:17,160
Don't ask.

311
00:17:17,510 --> 00:17:19,240
I skipped my physical check last month

312
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:20,400
just for the attendance bonus.

313
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,590
The report came back,

314
00:17:23,030 --> 00:17:24,510
and my wife

315
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:26,030
chewed me out.

316
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:28,110
She's still fuming.

317
00:17:28,110 --> 00:17:29,550
I wouldn't dare go home.

318
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,920
What show

319
00:17:37,350 --> 00:17:38,510
are you two putting on?

320
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,440
What else?

321
00:17:43,110 --> 00:17:44,200
The same old.

322
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:47,000
The clues from the case

323
00:17:47,550 --> 00:17:48,830
are all loose ends.

324
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:51,030
Nothing ties together.

325
00:17:51,590 --> 00:17:53,000
Everyone at Hongyun,

326
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,400
especially Wang Li,

327
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:57,200
has links to Bai.

328
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:59,160
But nothing shows

329
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:01,240
what they did in the Naked Banquet Case

330
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:02,440
15 years ago.

331
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:06,830
So we're discussing

332
00:18:07,350 --> 00:18:09,070
to see if there's something

333
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:10,340
that could tie things together.

334
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:14,000
Then infer it.

335
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:16,270
For us cops,

336
00:18:16,510 --> 00:18:18,590
not every case comes with solid proof.

337
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:20,040
We hypothesize.

338
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:21,640
Listen.

339
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,680
About this Naked Banquet Case,

340
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:25,350
I know every

341
00:18:25,590 --> 00:18:27,000
existing clue by heart.

342
00:18:29,830 --> 00:18:31,030
Here's the situation.

343
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:34,070
Wang Li,

344
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,480
the restaurant owner.

345
00:18:37,240 --> 00:18:38,510
What role could he play?

346
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,080
Organizer?

347
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:42,350
Unlikely.

348
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:45,160
Participant? Not high enough.

349
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:50,480
So maybe support staff.

350
00:18:51,790 --> 00:18:53,550
Restaurant support?

351
00:18:54,350 --> 00:18:55,590
Kitchen help?

352
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:58,720
Kitchen help from that restaurant?

353
00:18:59,110 --> 00:19:00,350
That fits.

354
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,400
Wild guessing?

355
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:06,160
Definitely not.

356
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:09,680
It's a bold assumption.

357
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:14,000
Basic detective work.

358
00:19:14,270 --> 00:19:15,480
Alright.

359
00:19:15,830 --> 00:19:16,920
Kitchen help.

360
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,480
My wife

361
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:31,680
just approved me going home.

362
00:19:32,510 --> 00:19:33,400
I'm heading out first.

363
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:34,910
Right.

364
00:19:35,350 --> 00:19:37,480
You two, stop arguing.

365
00:19:37,750 --> 00:19:38,960
Talk it out.

366
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,440
Alright.

367
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:41,800
I'm off.

368
00:19:47,790 --> 00:19:48,630
Right.

369
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:50,960
The files are in.

370
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:55,840
Here.

371
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,160
Be nice.

372
00:19:59,310 --> 00:20:00,550
No more arguing.

373
00:20:09,270 --> 00:20:10,400
Kitchen help?

374
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:14,160
Qin makes sense.

375
00:20:14,790 --> 00:20:16,160
You really buy that?

376
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:20,790
You believe that but not me?

377
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,240
Stop blinking.

378
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,590
Wang Yimo gets questioned tomorrow.

379
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:28,760
That's an order.

380
00:20:37,960 --> 00:20:39,240
Bad habit.

381
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:45,700
(Qingcheng Public Security Bureau)

382
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:47,590
Tang Tang.

383
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:53,110
Tang.

384
00:20:57,380 --> 00:21:04,340
(Qingcheng Public Security Bureau)

385
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:06,800
Oh right.

386
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:08,640
(Consecrated Amulet)

387
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:11,000
I got this amulet for you.

388
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:13,720
As a police officer, you face danger a lot.

389
00:21:14,830 --> 00:21:15,720
I'm giving this to you.

390
00:21:16,310 --> 00:21:17,440
Keep it on you.

391
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:18,470
It'll bring you good luck.

392
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:27,280
Thanks.

393
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:30,350
I should get going now.

394
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:31,960
Thanks for today.

395
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:45,300
Bye.

396
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:46,390
Bye.

397
00:21:51,550 --> 00:21:53,350
I heard from Wang you're leaving.

398
00:21:53,510 --> 00:21:54,550
You didn't mention it.

399
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:56,680
Yeah. My dad and I talked.

400
00:21:56,830 --> 00:21:58,310
Hongyun's been running for years.

401
00:21:58,310 --> 00:21:59,200
It was exhausting.

402
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:01,590
We've saved some money.

403
00:22:01,590 --> 00:22:02,750
I can earn now.

404
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:05,240
So I want him to move to a big city
and be with me.

405
00:22:06,510 --> 00:22:07,880
Your accountant, Zhang Ming,

406
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:09,920
heard from him lately?

407
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:12,110
Not for a few days.

408
00:22:13,030 --> 00:22:15,110
Since the restaurant closed,
I haven't gone there.

409
00:22:19,510 --> 00:22:20,640
Take a look at this.

410
00:22:22,270 --> 00:22:23,790
This is Zhang Ming's call record.

411
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,680
(Caller; Receiver; Qingcheng)
The day you almost got hurt,

412
00:22:26,030 --> 00:22:27,750
after I took the two livestream guys away,

413
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,790
you called Zhang Ming.

414
00:22:30,270 --> 00:22:31,200
What did you talk about?

415
00:22:34,750 --> 00:22:36,400
That day,

416
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:39,550
his mom's condition suddenly worsened.

417
00:22:39,550 --> 00:22:40,590
He needed money urgently.

418
00:22:40,750 --> 00:22:42,240
I called to ask

419
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:44,000
if he'd reached my dad.

420
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:46,240
It got resolved later.

421
00:22:50,160 --> 00:22:52,160
How well did you know Zhang Ming?

422
00:22:55,510 --> 00:22:57,920
He'd been at the restaurant over ten years.

423
00:22:58,240 --> 00:22:59,440
So I saw him often.

424
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:01,550
But you know, Ming

425
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:02,600
is devoted to his family.

426
00:23:03,310 --> 00:23:04,400
Especially for his mom.

427
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:06,640
He's given up a lot for her.

428
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:09,550
Once I overheard him on the phone.

429
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:11,310
Sounded like

430
00:23:11,830 --> 00:23:14,510
he was taking side jobs.

431
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:16,310
But I'm not sure

432
00:23:16,480 --> 00:23:17,750
about the specifics.

433
00:23:28,340 --> 00:23:29,500
(Qingcheng Public Security Bureau)

434
00:24:14,830 --> 00:24:15,670
Qiang.

435
00:24:16,240 --> 00:24:17,590
Yimo, go!

436
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,000
Go!

437
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:28,000
Qiang!

438
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:42,880
Go! Now!

439
00:25:16,590 --> 00:25:18,110
Excuse me.

440
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:19,480
Which room is Xu Qiang in?

441
00:25:19,830 --> 00:25:21,240
He just woke up.

442
00:25:21,350 --> 00:25:22,310
Over there. Room 31.

443
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:23,480
Thanks.

444
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:25,940
(Ward 4)

445
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,480
Qiang.

446
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:44,390
Bai…

447
00:25:46,160 --> 00:25:47,000
Bai…

448
00:25:48,550 --> 00:25:50,040
- Bai.
- What's with Bai?

449
00:25:54,030 --> 00:25:55,880
Ali, I...

450
00:26:00,470 --> 00:26:01,520
Bai...

451
00:26:03,010 --> 00:26:05,000
Bai's people are after Yimo.

452
00:26:06,110 --> 00:26:08,030
You were stabbed by his people?

453
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:15,110
Protect Yimo.

454
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:19,590
I will.

455
00:26:20,380 --> 00:26:22,550
Doctor, how is Xu Qiang?

456
00:26:23,350 --> 00:26:24,350
The wound is fairly deep,

457
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:26,240
but no major vessels were hit.

458
00:26:26,980 --> 00:26:28,060
There was blood loss,

459
00:26:28,230 --> 00:26:29,260
but he's safe now.

460
00:26:31,540 --> 00:26:32,820
When can he be discharged?

461
00:26:33,100 --> 00:26:34,060
We recommend

462
00:26:34,060 --> 00:26:35,860
two more days of observation.

463
00:26:36,020 --> 00:26:37,900
He's not stable yet.

464
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:41,380
Thank you, doctor.

465
00:26:54,260 --> 00:26:55,110
You are…

466
00:26:55,180 --> 00:26:56,780
Mr. Wang Li, right?

467
00:26:58,180 --> 00:26:59,040
And you are?

468
00:26:59,060 --> 00:26:59,900
Zhao Fengcheng.

469
00:27:00,460 --> 00:27:02,700
My partner Tang Tang mentions you often.

470
00:27:04,220 --> 00:27:05,060
Captain Zhao.

471
00:27:05,780 --> 00:27:06,980
Nice to meet you.

472
00:27:11,140 --> 00:27:12,580
Let's step outside for a quick chat.

473
00:27:24,900 --> 00:27:25,740
Sorry.

474
00:27:26,220 --> 00:27:28,980
(Student File; Wang Yimo; Birth Certificate)

475
00:27:35,260 --> 00:27:36,740
- Sorry.
- It's okay.

476
00:27:50,300 --> 00:27:52,060
Dad, how's Qiang?

477
00:27:55,020 --> 00:27:55,980
He was stabbed.

478
00:27:56,820 --> 00:27:57,660
He'll be fine.

479
00:27:57,820 --> 00:27:58,660
Really?

480
00:28:06,300 --> 00:28:07,140
Yimo,

481
00:28:08,580 --> 00:28:10,060
don't go anywhere.

482
00:28:11,740 --> 00:28:12,980
Be careful.

483
00:28:14,940 --> 00:28:17,580
This will be resolved soon.

484
00:28:19,420 --> 00:28:20,260
Dad,

485
00:28:21,060 --> 00:28:22,540
I went to the station today.

486
00:28:23,300 --> 00:28:24,820
I think Tang Tang and his team

487
00:28:25,020 --> 00:28:26,460
are already suspecting you.

488
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:30,540
I know. It's fine.

489
00:28:31,740 --> 00:28:32,620
I have a plan.

490
00:28:33,900 --> 00:28:35,020
What plan?

491
00:28:39,180 --> 00:28:40,740
This will be resolved soon.

492
00:28:40,740 --> 00:28:42,100
It'll be over.

493
00:28:43,340 --> 00:28:44,420
Trust me.

494
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:47,420
All I want

495
00:28:48,500 --> 00:28:49,540
is for you to be safe.

496
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:02,740
Zhang Ming?

497
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:05,140
Zhang Ming

498
00:29:06,420 --> 00:29:07,620
is a devoted son.

499
00:29:08,820 --> 00:29:10,820
His mom's been ill and in the hospital.

500
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:12,860
It costs a lot of money.

501
00:29:13,700 --> 00:29:14,780
After I shut the restaurant,

502
00:29:15,700 --> 00:29:16,900
the pressure on him got worse.

503
00:29:19,060 --> 00:29:20,740
We'd been friends for over ten years.

504
00:29:21,500 --> 00:29:22,660
I feel guilty.

505
00:29:22,660 --> 00:29:23,740
I couldn't help much.

506
00:29:24,260 --> 00:29:25,260
So after that,

507
00:29:27,180 --> 00:29:28,340
we hardly kept in touch.

508
00:29:28,950 --> 00:29:29,900
Haven't seen him since.

509
00:29:30,820 --> 00:29:32,340
When was the last time

510
00:29:32,340 --> 00:29:33,300
you saw him?

511
00:29:38,500 --> 00:29:39,780
Are you interrogating me?

512
00:29:41,020 --> 00:29:41,860
No.

513
00:29:42,220 --> 00:29:43,780
Just getting some info.

514
00:29:53,380 --> 00:29:54,220
Ali,

515
00:29:54,780 --> 00:29:56,180
I know you want to find Bai.

516
00:29:56,820 --> 00:29:57,740
A few days ago,

517
00:29:58,100 --> 00:29:59,220
I found a chance

518
00:29:59,580 --> 00:30:01,100
to check his location.

519
00:30:01,940 --> 00:30:03,340
Not long after I left,

520
00:30:04,300 --> 00:30:05,380
Li Xu showed up.

521
00:30:09,620 --> 00:30:10,460
I think

522
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:13,700
they're planning something against you.

523
00:30:21,860 --> 00:30:22,700
Li Tong,

524
00:30:23,460 --> 00:30:24,860
when you found Bai,

525
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:27,820
why didn't you tell me right away?

526
00:30:30,460 --> 00:30:31,580
I wanted to.

527
00:30:35,030 --> 00:30:36,460
I was afraid you'd go after him alone

528
00:30:37,020 --> 00:30:37,860
and get hurt.

529
00:30:38,970 --> 00:30:40,020
You know what Bai's like.

530
00:30:40,020 --> 00:30:41,020
So do I.

531
00:30:41,860 --> 00:30:42,710
Besides,

532
00:30:42,740 --> 00:30:44,060
he's got Caicai right by his side.

533
00:30:46,820 --> 00:30:47,660
Ali,

534
00:30:48,660 --> 00:30:49,900
don't do anything reckless.

535
00:30:54,260 --> 00:30:55,780
Send me Bai's location.

536
00:30:57,940 --> 00:31:00,100
Yimo's safety matters more than my life.

537
00:32:01,660 --> 00:32:05,180
(Resident ID)

538
00:33:59,020 --> 00:33:59,860
Master,

539
00:34:01,020 --> 00:34:03,220
the substation sent the footage
of Xu Qiang's stabbing.

540
00:34:03,700 --> 00:34:05,220
It's in the old neighborhood

541
00:34:05,220 --> 00:34:06,260
two blocks away.

542
00:34:06,540 --> 00:34:07,620
No cameras inside the alley.

543
00:34:07,690 --> 00:34:09,250
Wang Yimo's caught on the entrance feed,

544
00:34:09,300 --> 00:34:10,380
and that unidentified guy

545
00:34:10,380 --> 00:34:11,740
went in right after her.

546
00:34:12,220 --> 00:34:14,740
At the time of the attack,

547
00:34:14,940 --> 00:34:16,540
Wang Yimo ran out first,

548
00:34:16,540 --> 00:34:17,620
then the guy.

549
00:34:17,700 --> 00:34:19,540
A passerby found Xu Qiang

550
00:34:19,540 --> 00:34:20,380
and called it in.

551
00:34:22,300 --> 00:34:23,420
So close to us.

552
00:34:23,940 --> 00:34:24,780
That's way too bold.

553
00:34:27,780 --> 00:34:29,140
Does the unidentified guy

554
00:34:29,140 --> 00:34:29,980
look like him?

555
00:34:34,260 --> 00:34:35,100
Yes.

556
00:34:36,580 --> 00:34:37,740
I think it's the same guy.

557
00:34:40,340 --> 00:34:41,780
If so,

558
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:46,980
his target may be Wang Yimo.

559
00:34:48,260 --> 00:34:49,420
Do you still think

560
00:34:49,980 --> 00:34:51,940
she has nothing to do with this?

561
00:34:57,740 --> 00:34:58,580
What now?

562
00:34:59,370 --> 00:35:00,460
Every time she's mentioned,

563
00:35:00,900 --> 00:35:01,940
you react like this.

564
00:35:04,220 --> 00:35:05,340
No, Master.

565
00:35:06,340 --> 00:35:07,180
The whole thing

566
00:35:07,940 --> 00:35:09,580
just freaks me out.

567
00:35:12,340 --> 00:35:14,460
Everyone we've spotted lately

568
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:16,180
is now connected somehow.

569
00:35:18,980 --> 00:35:20,660
Something's about to happen.

570
00:35:22,220 --> 00:35:23,060
Captain Zhao.

571
00:35:23,380 --> 00:35:24,220
A skeleton

572
00:35:24,540 --> 00:35:26,580
was found by the road near Shanquan Village.

573
00:35:46,260 --> 00:35:47,110
Captain Zhao.

574
00:35:47,180 --> 00:35:49,060
Road maintenance found a bag

575
00:35:49,140 --> 00:35:50,700
this morning and reported it.

576
00:35:59,460 --> 00:36:01,580
Captain Zhao, it's found during inspection.

577
00:36:02,540 --> 00:36:04,740
(Liu Xijun)

578
00:36:22,420 --> 00:36:25,500
(Police)

579
00:36:34,700 --> 00:36:35,540
Mr. Wang,

580
00:36:36,140 --> 00:36:37,300
Bai's been found.

581
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:38,780
He told me

582
00:36:39,980 --> 00:36:42,140
he wants to throw another banquet

583
00:36:43,420 --> 00:36:44,540
just for you.

584
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:08,300
Yimo.

585
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:20,540
Don't get up. Stay still.

586
00:37:21,900 --> 00:37:22,980
Why are you here?

587
00:37:28,100 --> 00:37:28,940
Qiang.

588
00:37:29,900 --> 00:37:30,860
I'm sorry.

589
00:37:32,860 --> 00:37:34,700
You got hurt because of me.

590
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:39,580
It's okay.

591
00:37:42,140 --> 00:37:43,180
That day,

592
00:37:43,620 --> 00:37:45,020
why were you there?

593
00:37:46,780 --> 00:37:48,700
Your dad said

594
00:37:49,820 --> 00:37:51,380
you might be in danger.

595
00:37:53,540 --> 00:37:54,820
I wanted to protect you.

596
00:38:02,860 --> 00:38:03,700
Yimo,

597
00:38:05,220 --> 00:38:06,340
you should go home.

598
00:38:08,140 --> 00:38:09,660
Stay there.

599
00:38:10,820 --> 00:38:11,660
Don't go out.

600
00:38:12,260 --> 00:38:14,060
If anything feels off,

601
00:38:14,060 --> 00:38:14,900
just

602
00:38:15,660 --> 00:38:17,660
call the police.

603
00:38:18,140 --> 00:38:19,660
Tang Tang, right?

604
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:24,180
He truly wants to help you.

605
00:38:27,020 --> 00:38:28,180
I can tell.

606
00:38:31,540 --> 00:38:32,380
Yimo,

607
00:38:34,540 --> 00:38:35,380
don't cry.

608
00:38:38,220 --> 00:38:39,060
Don't cry.

609
00:38:44,660 --> 00:38:46,060
For me, it's not worth it.

610
00:38:50,180 --> 00:38:51,020
Qiang...

611
00:38:51,900 --> 00:38:52,740
Yimo.

612
00:38:54,700 --> 00:38:55,540
Go.

613
00:40:30,060 --> 00:40:31,820
Everything gets pricier around New Year.

614
00:40:35,980 --> 00:40:36,820
Look.

615
00:40:36,940 --> 00:40:38,500
This isn't the kid from before.

616
00:40:38,980 --> 00:40:40,860
Something's definitely off with them.

617
00:40:41,220 --> 00:40:42,060
Right?

618
00:40:50,380 --> 00:40:52,100
Pig trotter soup's ready.

619
00:40:52,540 --> 00:40:53,380
Here you go.

620
00:40:57,460 --> 00:40:58,300
What's on your mind?

621
00:40:59,340 --> 00:41:01,660
My teacher assigned an essay.

622
00:41:01,860 --> 00:41:02,780
The topic is

623
00:41:02,940 --> 00:41:03,900
"My Dad."

624
00:41:04,220 --> 00:41:05,100
That's a good one.

625
00:41:05,660 --> 00:41:06,860
What are you going to write?

626
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:07,900
I've got it.

627
00:41:08,100 --> 00:41:09,140
I wrote that my dad is

628
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:11,860
a food magician.

629
00:41:12,020 --> 00:41:13,620
In our tiny Kitchen,

630
00:41:13,700 --> 00:41:15,940
he can whip up a table
full of my favorite dishes.

631
00:41:17,140 --> 00:41:18,460
That's my one big talent

632
00:41:18,580 --> 00:41:19,620
and you found that.

633
00:41:20,140 --> 00:41:21,420
I also wrote,

634
00:41:21,620 --> 00:41:23,780
my dad is the bravest person.

635
00:41:24,380 --> 00:41:25,420
When him around,

636
00:41:25,420 --> 00:41:26,620
I'm not afraid of anything.

637
00:41:28,540 --> 00:41:29,380
Try it.

638
00:41:36,540 --> 00:41:37,940
Dad, it's tasty.

639
00:41:39,460 --> 00:41:41,300
Then I'll make it for you every day.

640
00:41:43,380 --> 00:41:45,020
Pig trotter soup's ready.

641
00:41:52,180 --> 00:41:53,060
What's on your mind?

642
00:42:07,180 --> 00:42:08,020
Dad,

643
00:42:09,900 --> 00:42:11,420
thank you for everything.

644
00:42:12,500 --> 00:42:14,740
Being your daughter these years

645
00:42:15,140 --> 00:42:16,180
has made me happy.

646
00:42:17,900 --> 00:42:19,280
Why bring this up all of a sudden?

647
00:42:27,540 --> 00:42:28,380
Tasty.

648
00:42:29,820 --> 00:42:30,850
Then I'll make it for you

649
00:42:31,660 --> 00:42:32,620
every day.

650
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:52,280
♪Dreams of the past sleep in the chill♪

651
00:42:52,280 --> 00:42:55,720
♪Now I run toward the light♪

652
00:42:57,560 --> 00:43:02,840
♪What does the fire burn,
what does it reveal?♪

653
00:43:03,160 --> 00:43:06,800
♪Is the answer found when the sun rises♪

654
00:43:07,400 --> 00:43:11,720
♪If it's all a lie♪

655
00:43:12,880 --> 00:43:17,080
♪Should I tear it open?♪

656
00:43:18,400 --> 00:43:23,120
♪If it's all part of the journey♪

657
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:28,640
♪Then face the blaze head-on♪

658
00:43:29,040 --> 00:43:33,520
♪Let the sun awaken my heart's crave♪

659
00:43:34,040 --> 00:43:39,760
♪Pain reminds me I'm alive♪

660
00:43:39,880 --> 00:43:44,720
♪The world can't take away every clear sky♪

661
00:43:45,360 --> 00:43:50,520
♪The hotter it gets, the fiercer I fight♪

662
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:55,520
♪Let the sun burn away all I lean upon♪

663
00:43:55,880 --> 00:44:01,520
♪Leave me only what endures♪

664
00:44:01,640 --> 00:44:07,200
♪At the cliff's edge, all fear shatters♪

665
00:44:07,240 --> 00:44:14,200
♪With a grounded heart, a soul like fire♪
